Package Shared

Class User

  • java.lang.Object
    • Shared.User
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    Professor, Student

    public class User
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    Provides data fields and methods to create a Java data-type, representing a User in a Java application. The overall purpose of this class exercise is to build useful objects for a Learning platform built for students and professors for the final project of ENSF409.
    Since:
    March 31st 2018
    Version:
    1.0
    Author:
    M.Amouzai, A.Benaceur
